# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated code that should NOT be committed
# (Note: protobuf-generated Go code IS committed by policy — see ADR/Phase 3)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# sqlc generates Go code that IS committed under internal/storage/queries/
# Reserved here in case future generated artifacts are excluded.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets and credentials (defensive — never commit secrets)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*-jwt-secret
secrets.yaml
credentials.json
service-account.json
kubeconfig
.kube/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Load test artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
tests/load/results/
tests/load/*.csv
tests/load/*.json

# Compiled DAG artifacts from example projects (regenerated by `leoflow compile`)
examples/**/dag.json

# Throwaway UI audit / API-capture artifacts (never commit; use docs/reference/ for curated fixtures)
/audit_data/
/airflow__*.json
/leoflow__*.json
/capture_ui.py
/compare_apis.py
/compare_json.py
/deep_diff.py
/full_comparison.py
/interactive_audit.py

# Generated by `leoflow dev`/`compile` inside user DAG projects
dags/**/Dockerfile
dags/**/dag.json
